{"type":"system","subtype":"task_progress","task_id":"a6218a8e7da50ea0f","tool_use_id":"toolu_01TyVq55huB8WDwxXQnVa2vD","description":"Writing patches/infra/dockerfile-rules.md","usage":{"total_tokens":34945,"tool_uses":14,"duration_ms":42125},"last_tool_name":"Write","uuid":"bf3e0fc9-a7ca-4952-88f8-f48b82f53eb6","session_id":"d06dabce-ed3c-4abf-ad84-f2845532d39a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01WUJgfnPww2g9sXR5xW4yLt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01UDPEqeQFpQpd6B9xLVyftb","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/patches/infra/dockerfile-rules.md","content":"# Dockerfile Rules\n\nRequired elements for production Dockerfiles. The `validateDockerfile()` function\nchecks each category and reports gaps through the audit infrastructure dimension.\n\n## 1. Pinned Base Image (pinned-from)\n\nAll `FROM` instructions must use a specific version tag or digest.\n\n- **Pass:** `FROM node:22-slim`, `FROM python:3.12-alpine`, `FROM node@sha256:abc123`\n- **Fail:** `FROM node:latest`, `FROM node` (no tag)\n\n## 2. Project Binary on PATH (binary-installed)\n\nThe container must install the project binary so it is available on PATH.\n\n- **Pass:** `RUN npm install -g <package>`, `RUN pip install <package>`, `COPY --from=builder /app/bin /usr/local/bin`\n- **Fail:** No install command for the project binary\n\n## 3. Verification Tools (verification-tools)\n\nContainers must include `curl` and `jq` for health checks and debugging.\n\n- **Pass:** `RUN apt-get install -y curl jq`, `RUN apk add --no-cache curl jq`\n- **Fail:** Missing `curl` or `jq` installation\n\n## 4. No Source Code Copy (no-source-copy)\n\nContainers should use build artifacts, not raw source code.\n\n- **Pass:** `COPY dist/ /app/dist/`, `COPY --from=builder /app/dist /app`\n- **Fail:** `COPY src/ /app/src/`, `COPY lib/ /app/lib/`, `COPY test/ /app/test/`\n\n## 5. Non-Root User (non-root-user)\n\nContainers must run as a non-root user.\n\n- **Pass:** `USER node`, `USER appuser`\n- **Fail:** No `USER` instruction, or only `USER root`\n\n## 6. Cache Cleanup (cache-cleanup)\n\nPackage manager caches must be cleaned to reduce image size.\n\n- **Pass:** `rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*`, `npm cache clean --force`, `pip cache purge`\n- **Fail:** No cache cleanup after package installation\n\n## Project-Type-Specific Notes\n\n### Node.js\n\n- Use `node:<version>-slim` or `node:<version>-alpine` base images\n- Install production binary with `npm install -g`\n- Clean npm cache: `npm cache clean --force`\n\n### Python\n\n- Use `python:<version>-slim` or `python:<version>-alpine` base images\n- Install with `pip install --no-cache-dir` or run `pip cache purge`\n- Use virtual environments in the container\n\n### Plugin (Claude Code)\n\n- Plugins are git-based, not containerized -- Dockerfile rules apply only to npm distribution\n- If a Dockerfile is present, all 6 rules apply\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":114,"cache_read_input_tokens":34759,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":114,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01TyVq55huB8WDwxXQnVa2vD","session_id":"d06dabce-ed3c-4abf-ad84-f2845532d39a","uuid":"196eead9-3d94-40f1-9228-9d67aafbb149"}
